original_title: Tom Petty & the Heartbreakers - High Grass Dogs - Live from the Fillmore
overview: High Grass Dogs - Live at the Fillmore features 19 songs performed by Tom Petty and the Heartbreakers at the Fillmore in March 1999, from performances on March 15th and March 16th of that year.
title: Tom Petty & the Heartbreakers - High Grass Dogs - Live from the Fillmore
